transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, this is Jimmy, how can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Hi, Jimmy, how's your day going, bud?

Speaker 1: It's going pretty good, how about you?

Speaker 2: Good, good, thank you.

Speaker 1: I just recently put in an order for your new Viagra,

Speaker 2: and it got to the point where it asked me to put a password in,

Speaker 1: and it already, for some reason, already had a password,

Speaker 2: which I did not put in, and now I'm stuck,

Speaker 1: even though I've given my credit card number, my address, and all that stuff.

Speaker 2: So I don't know what password is in there, because I didn't put one in.

Speaker 1: And I put a password in that I usually use when I buy an online product,

Speaker 2: and so it doesn't recognize that,

Speaker 1: because I really never had a chance to put a password in.

Speaker 2: Not a problem.

Speaker 1: So you tell me what it is.

Speaker 2: Is this Clyde?

Speaker 1: Go ahead.

Speaker 2: Is this Clyde that I'm speaking to?

Speaker 1: Yes, Clyde Daig.

Speaker 2: Hey, Clyde, I do have your information up.

Speaker 1: I do see that your order was placed.

Speaker 2: I'm glad you called, though, because that's always the best way to do it,

Speaker 1: because you're trying to get the AGB, is that correct?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And it looks like that you put in for the 50 milligrams?

Speaker 1: Yes, that's correct.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: I have a recommendation for you.

Speaker 2: You know, I think if you go with the 100 milligrams,

Speaker 1: you'll probably be more satisfied with that one,

Speaker 2: and, plus, if that one's too strong for you, what a lot of people do,

Speaker 1: Clyde, they just break it in half.

Speaker 2: And it's the same thing as the 50 milligrams.

Speaker 1: Okay, so, yeah, if you break it in half, I understand.

Speaker 2: Well, I already have a prescription from my doctor for 50 milligrams,

Speaker 1: and if this is more potent than the old Viagra, I may split it in half

Speaker 2: and make it a 25.

Speaker 1: I got you.

Speaker 2: I'm just sharing with you how a lot of people work it,

Speaker 1: so I just thought I would share that with you.

Speaker 2: Yeah, and I've done that before, but I've never gotten a 100.

Speaker 1: I've always gotten 50 and split those in half.

Speaker 2: But let's just go ahead and go with the 50, and if it comes over well

Speaker 1: and everything's working, next time I'll order 100.

Speaker 2: Okay, because that's what your prescription is going to have.

Speaker 1: It's going to have the 50 on it.

Speaker 2: That's fine.

Speaker 1: Okay, so the order was placed and it was done.

Speaker 2: As far as your password is concerned,

Speaker 1: I would recommend that you just give us a call when you're ready to order,

Speaker 2: because a lot of times when you're online, a lot of things get mixed up and stuff.

Speaker 1: But it's up to you as far as you say you can't get the password.

Speaker 2: Well, I'm fine with calling you guys and ordering it that way.

Speaker 1: I've already written your phone number down.

Speaker 2: Well, it's actually saved in my phone.

Speaker 1: But that would be preferable because I don't like using passwords all the time.

Speaker 2: I'd rather talk with a real person.

Speaker 1: I understand, and that's not a problem.

Speaker 2: So we went ahead and I see your order, so okay.

Speaker 1: So you're good.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: All right, fantastic.

Speaker 2: So I didn't see a shipping charge.

Speaker 1: It must be free shipping.

Speaker 2: Is that correct?

Speaker 1: No, it's not free shipping, unfortunately.

Speaker 2: So the actual total, I'll tell you right now,

Speaker 1: because I see you upgraded for the additional five pills for the 1470.

Speaker 2: So I'll tell you what the actual total that you're going to see.

Speaker 1: Bear with me one second.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Sure.

Speaker 2: The 1470.

Speaker 1: How much?

Speaker 2: So it's going to be a total of $78.65.

Speaker 1: That includes shipping.

Speaker 2: The shipping cost is a tracking number, so you know that it's getting there.

Speaker 1: That's fine.

Speaker 2: How much is the shipping, just out of curiosity?

Speaker 1: Yeah, the shipping is usually $9.95.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: I'm sorry, $13.95.

Speaker 1: $13.95.

Speaker 2: Because for the original tin, it's $63.95.

Speaker 1: For the original tin, it's the additional 1470.

Speaker 2: Okay?

Speaker 1: All right, and the total amount again, please?

Speaker 2: $78.65.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Okay, we're good.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: I appreciate your help.

Speaker 1: All right, no problem.

Speaker 2: Take care.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
